            </div>
            <div type="factoid" uri="http://syriaca.org/spear/3136-10" resp="#syoung">
                <listEvent>
                    <event>
                        <desc>
                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/51">Severus</persName>appeals to<persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/511">Gregory of<placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/2693">Nazianzus</placeName></persName>to prove the efficacy of the Eucharist regardless of its administrator. Just as Baptism is valid regardless of the priest, and the seal of the king is valid regardless if it's set it in gold or wax, so the Eucharist is efficacious regardless of the priest.
                        </desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/greek-father http://syriaca.org/keyword/seals http://syriaca.org/keyword/baptism http://syriaca.org/keyword/theology"/>
